    ],
    "http://schema.org/name": [
      {
        "@value": "Green Room Session with YASSiN & Sean Terrio"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@value": "<p>YASSiN & Sean Terrio are back on the East Coast, first bringing their high energy and soulful sounds to New Glasgow! Last June, they travelled to Halifax, Nova Scotia for the first time with their band and fell in love with this part of the country, and all of their fans in the area. Fast forward almost one year later, they did not hesitate to make another appearance, and are looking forward to making more memories and connections as they sing their hearts out for you! If you're looking for a great time, great music, and great hair - come to the show, and see what this dynamic band is all about! </p>\n\n<style>\n.location-page-temp {display: block!important;}\n</style>\n\n"
      }
