    "http://schema.org/name": [
      {
        "@value": "Symply Skynyrd"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@value": "<p><b>The Lynyrd Skynyrd Tribute</b></p>\n\n<p>Symply Skynyrd Canada's authentic Lynyrd Skynyrd delivering the sound and energy of Lynyrd Skynyrd since 2017, while earning a world-class reputation across the nation. A powerful performance that hits the bullseye! <br>\nSimply Skynyrd - The Lynyrd Skynyrd Tribute show delivers an electrifying live concert experience, celebrating the legendary Southern rock sound of Lynyrd Skynyrd. Playing at theaters, festivals, and special events, Symply Skynyrd captures the spirit of Skynyrd's iconic live performances with precision and passion.</p>\n\n<p>The band's repertoire spans Skynyrd's chart-topping hits and fan favourites, offering a show that resonates with both casual listeners and devoted fans. Each member is a true Southern rock enthusiast, committed to honouring the legacy of Lynyrd Skynyrd through authentic sound, energy, and performance.</p>\n\n<p><b>Symply Skynyrd - The truly authentic tribute to Lynyrd Skynyrd.</b></p>\n\n"
      }
    ],
